<plot>A young football player of Olympiakos, who works at a gas station, becomes engaged to a poor clerk, Christina, but is severely injured in a match -which keeps him away from the football fields and his job. Now, out of work, he faces crushing financial difficulties; Christina, however, stands by his side, and in the end the couple manages to get back onto their feet.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?025648</url></doc>
